column2: SELECT s.specobjid, s.ra, s.dec, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, g.lgm_tot_p5#, m.logMass FROM #upload u JOIN SpecObjAll s ON (s.plate = u.up_plate AND s.mjd = u.up_mjd AND s.fiberID = u.up_fiber) JOIN galSpecExtra g ON g.specObjID = s.specObjID JOIN stellarMassPassivePort m ON m.specObjID = s.specObjID ORDER by x.up_id ##', @log = #, @filter = #
